        </ul>
        <div class="tier-urgency">
          🎯 <strong>Target Rp 50jt</strong> • Terkumpul Rp 12jt (24%)
        </div>
        <a href="https://wa.me/6282234551160?text=Assalamualaikum%2C%20saya%20ingin%20berkontribusi%20untuk%20program%20Wakaf%20Produktif%20Koperasi%20Yayasan.%20Mohon%20info%20lengkapnya." class="btn btn-outline w-full" target="_blank">💬 Kontribusi via WhatsApp →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="donate-alt">
