          </div>
          <p class="qris-note">Minta QRIS live via WhatsApp admin</p>
          <a href="https://wa.me/6282234551160?text=Assalamualaikum%2C%20saya%20ingin%20QRIS%20untuk%20donasi%20YPSMA." target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="display:inline-block;margin-top:.5rem;background:var(--green);color:#fff;padding:.5em 1em;border-radius:8px;font-size:.85rem;font-weight:600;">💬 Minta QRIS via WA →</a>
